VTX CDC track merger

This README describes how to train and validate the neural network based VTX CDC Merger
module on simulated Belle II data.

Usage:

export BELLE2_VTX_UPGRADE_GT=upgrade_vtx_5layer_v3_2022-12-05
export BELLE2_VTX_BACKGROUND_DIR=/home/benjamin/b2/bg_v3/


basf2 collect_data.py -n 2000 -- --outputdir=/path/to/folder

python3 train.py  --inputdir=/path/to/folder  --checkpoint=/path/to/checkpoint

copy checkpoint dir to default location

b2validation -s fullTrackingValidationVTXBkg_NNMERGER.py